This is a placeholder file. The actual Iron Man clap sound will be generated or sourced.
For now, you can replace this with any short sound effect (repulsor blast, arc reactor hum, etc.)

To add a real sound:
1. Find a royalty-free Iron Man sound effect (repulsor, arc reactor, suit activation)
2. Convert to MP3 format
3. Replace this file with the actual audio file
4. Recommended duration: 0.5-1.5 seconds

Suggested sources:
- Freesound.org
- Zapsplat.com
- YouTube Audio Library (download and convert)
